details.description: An extraordinary opportunity to own one of Worcester’s premier estates in a neighborhood of distinguished custom homes. Enter through the grand center foyer with its sweeping bridal staircase and be captivated by timeless architectural details blended with modern refinement. The formal fireplaced living room, expansive dining room, and paneled library offer sophistication for entertaining, while the brand-new designer kitchen with marble floors and breakfast room elevates everyday living. With 4 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, dual staircases, hardwood floors, and a lavish primary suite boasting 5 closets, no detail has been overlooked. Relax in the heated sunroom, host on the stunning patio, and enjoy beautifully landscaped grounds. A lower-level bonus room and ample storage complete this exceptional residence. Perfectly situated with convenient access to cultural landmarks, fine dining, and travel, this is a rare offering for the discerning buyer.

details.description: Welcome to 33 Aylesbury Road in the highly sought after Salisbury Street neighborhood. This 5,400 sq ft mid-century modern gem, custom-designed by Irwin Regent, showcases exquisite craftsmanship throughout. From its striking brick exterior and elegant curved walls to luxurious hardware, custom flooring, and built-ins, every detail impresses. The formal living room stuns with 17-foot ceilings and oversized sliders that blend indoor and outdoor living. The family room features a custom bar, brick accent wall, and built-in entertainment center. The sleek kitchen offers high-gloss cabinetry, granite counters, and updated appliances. A private office with bath provides a quiet retreat. The primary suite spans its own level with a spa-like bath, dressing room, and ample closets. Upstairs are three spacious bedrooms and two full baths. Enjoy serene moments by your private brook and pond or host unforgettable gatherings in style.

details.description: Presenting "The George Gabriel House," an exceptional property renowned as one of the area's original and most distinguished residences. This impressive 7-bedroom home, offers unparalleled luxury and historic charm, and boasts original architectural details: murals, leaded glass, and pocket doors. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary dream, featuring granite counters, top-of-the-line pro appliances, gas range, double ovens and a bright and airy breakfast nook – the perfect spot to start your day. Indulge in sophisticated living spaces, from the formal living rooms ideal for hosting memorable events to the distinguished study for quiet reflection. The magnificent great room, with an inviting fireplace and walls of French doors serves as a central gathering space and provides effortless flow to the patio, gunite pool, hot tub, and garden. Lower level game room, bar & walkout. Hardwood floors, 2-car garage with an attached shed. This is a rare opportunity in Worcester's premier neighborhood.
